=== Ganglia Monitoring Script ===

Ganglia Monitor Script is an easy way to
add value to monitor for gmond.


You can add/edit/remove script. They are
located in the 
/usr/share/ganglia-monitor-script/script
directory.


You've made change in the script:

If the service ganglia-monitor-script is
running you don't have to restart it.
It'll scan the directory itself every
60 secondes.
